{"data":{"properties":{"created_at":1626291196000,"custom_properties":{},"events":{},"identifier":"layouts/spacer","modified_at":1636941863000,"properties":{"Spacer":[{"name":"is","description":"<p>Renders the <code>Spacer</code> as a block (<code>div</code>) or inline (<code>span</code>).</p>\n","default":"div","types":["div","span"]},{"name":"spacing","description":"<p>Adjusts the visual spacing between the two immediate siblings of the <code>Spacer</code>.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge","{VIEWPORT}:{SPACING}"]},{"name":"spacing_x","description":"<p>Adjusts the horizontal visual spacing between the two immediate siblings of the <code>Spacer</code>.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge","{VIEWPORT}:{SPACING}"]},{"name":"spacing_y","description":"<p>Adjusts the vertical visual spacing between the two immediate siblings of the <code>Spacer</code>.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge","{VIEWPORT}:{SPACING}"]}]},"sections":[{"identifier":"spacer","level":1,"text":"Spacer"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"spacing","level":2,"text":"Spacing"},{"identifier":"inline","level":2,"text":"Inline"}],"slots":{},"snippets":[{"identifier":"spacer-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Box,\n        Spacer,\n        Stack,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Box\n    palette=\"inverse\"\n    padding_x=\"small\"\n    padding_y=\"tiny\"\n>\n    <Stack orientation=\"horizontal\">\n        LEFT\n        <Spacer />\n        RIGHT\n    </Stack>\n</Box>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Spacer Preview"},{"identifier":"spacer-imports","script":"<script>\n    import {Spacer} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>","syntax":"html","title":"Spacer Imports"},{"identifier":"spacer-spacing","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Box,\n        Spacer,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">TINY</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            TOP\n            <Spacer spacing=\"tiny\" />\n            BOTTOM\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">SMALL</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            TOP\n            <Spacer spacing=\"small\" />\n            BOTTOM\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">MEDIUM</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            TOP\n            <Spacer spacing=\"medium\" />\n            BOTTOM\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">LARGE</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            TOP\n            <Spacer spacing=\"large\" />\n            BOTTOM\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">HUGE</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            TOP\n            <Spacer spacing=\"huge\" />\n            BOTTOM\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n</Stack>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Spacer Spacing"},{"identifier":"spacer-inline","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Box,\n        Spacer,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">BLOCK / DIV / DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            margin_top=\"small\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            TOP\n            <Spacer spacing=\"huge\" />\n            BOTTOM\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">INLINE / SPAN</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"inverse\"\n            margin_top=\"small\"\n            padding_x=\"small\"\n            padding_y=\"tiny\"\n        >\n            LEFT\n            <Spacer\n                is=\"span\"\n                orientation=\"horizontal\"\n                spacing=\"huge\"\n            />\n            RIGHT\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n</Stack>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Spacer Inline"}],"title":"Spacer"},"render":"<h1 id=\"spacer\">Spacer</h1>\n<p><code>Spacer</code> is a layout primitive that takes up all available space between its two immediate siblings.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/spacer/spacer-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/spacer/spacer-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Spacer<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"spacing\">Spacing</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsitivity\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>spacing={[&quot;medium&quot;, &quot;tablet:small&quot;, &quot;mobile:tiny&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can adjust the spacing between the immediate siblings via the <code>spacing</code>, <code>spacing_x</code>, and <code>spacing_y</code> properties.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/spacer/spacer-spacing?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/spacer/spacer-spacing?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"inline\">Inline</h2>\n<p>You can have the <code>Spacer</code> rendering as an inline <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> via the <code>is</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/spacer/spacer-inline?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/spacer/spacer-inline?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}